ůKENNETH MCLENNAN HAY, ESQ, B.E.M., K.C.L.J., F.S.A. Scot.
20th FEBRUARY, 1918 22nd SEPTEMBER, 1992.
COMMISSIONER OF THE CLAN HAY 1979-1990.
PRESIDENT OF THE ST ANDREWS SOCIETY OF EDINBURGH.
CHAIRMAN - THE ROYAL CELTIC SOCIETY
A GOVERNOR OF BENENDEN HOSPITAL.
ERECTED BY HIS FAMILY, HIS MANY FRIENDS
AND THE SOCIETIES AND TRUSTS THAT HE SERVED SO WELL.
SERVA IUGUM"Ģ
